    section(data-hex="D52D39", id="pudding-monsters").review.review--portrait.review--text--light.review--phone--light
      .wrapper
        .review__images
          .review__image__wrapper
            ul.slides
              li
                img(src="/imgs/pudding-monsters/pudding-monsters-1.jpg")
              li
                img(src="/imgs/pudding-monsters/pudding-monsters-2.jpg")
              li
                img(src="/imgs/pudding-monsters/pudding-monsters-3.jpg")
        .review__desc
          h2 Pudding Monsters
          p
            | Creating a follow up up to the classic Cut The Rope game is no easy feat, 
            | however Zepto seem to taken it in their stride here and have created another 
            | classic.
          p
            | The great illustration and animation you would expect has been packed together 
            | with varying game play through a collection of worlds each bringing a new 
            | power of its own.
          a(href="http://www.puddingmonsters.com/").btn View app

