            | Lumosity is very polished brain training game thats aims to improve your 
            | mental ability through a variety of different mental tasks.
          p
            | This game does offer absorbing and engaging gameplay that will keep you 
            | coming back again and again.
          a(href="https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/lumosity-mobile/id577232024?mt=8").btn View App



