        .review__desc
          h2 Thing List
          p
            | Built by the ever admirable 
            a(href="http://www.elepath.com/") Elepath. 
            | Thinglist is a todo list app focused around categories, to quickly take notes 
            | when someone mentions something of interest in conversation whether thats 
            | "A strange new restaurant. A book with a nice cover. A far-out dancer."
          p
            | A simple layout aids a very enjoy experience and while it lacks more advanced 
            | features, I've never found myself to notice.
          a(href="http://getthinglist.com/").btn View App



